# TodoMVC React — Project Memory

This is what `/init` should produce (tweak to match reality).

## Stack
- React 17 (upgrade target for Track A: React 18+)
- Jest + React Testing Library
- CRA or Vite (confirm)

## Commands
- `npm ci`, `npm test`, `npm run lint`, `npm run build`, `npm run dev`

## Conventions
- Components in `src/components/`
- Co-located `*.test.jsx` or `*.test.tsx`

## Known pitfalls
- TodoMVC spec tests are strict — don't change URL fragment routing
- Current canonical example has no persistence (`useReducer` only) — adding it is a valid Track B feature

## Don't touch
- `node_modules/`, `build/`, `dist/`
